# GoldFish standards

- Prefer **clarity + correctness**, then optimize hot paths with measurements.
- Keep request handlers **thin**; move business logic to `goldfish-core`, storage to `goldfish-storage`.
- Use `anyhow` only at app boundaries; use typed errors (`thiserror`) inside libraries.
- Every external call (DB/HTTP/cache) must have **timeouts**, **bounded concurrency**, and **structured tracing**.
- No blocking on async threads (no sync I/O in handlers); use `spawn_blocking` when unavoidable.
- Expose **OpenAPI** at `/api/spec` and **Swagger UI** at `/swaggerui/`.
